name: Chris Hemsworth Embedding for 2.1
description:
Chris Hemsworth Textual Inversion for SD 2.1

In my never ending quest to cast my own movie here is Thor himself. All photos are from movies not press events so they are grittier and more dramatic in the outputs.

Works very well in my testing and plays well with other embeddings. All raw text2img examples.

Enjoy and please comment pics of what you make with it!

modelVersions.name: chrshmswrth
modelVersions.description:
Version 1. Trained on 31 images with a batch size of 11 and gradient accumulation of 3.

Learning rate: 0.05:10, 0.02:20, 0.01:60, 0.005:200, 0.002:500, 0.001:3000, 0.0005
